title: 2 Homes + Ocean View In Sunny Smith River 4.58 acres,
text:
2 Homes + Ocean View In Sunny Smith River 4.58 acres, ad date: 09/30/2015 
Ocean View In Sunny Smith River 4.58 acres, your own little slice of heaven with a 2-bed + bonus/2- bath home, 1,680 sq. ft. PLUS a 1/1 home, 360 sq. ft. and a 4-car garage; seasonal creek cascades in rear of property where ferns, trees, moss-covered boulders, and wildlife abound. RV hook-ups, possible lot split, plenty of paved parking for your toys, newer roof, remodeling/more!
